      "title": "More than 1.5mn litrs of fuel distributed so far: LIOC MD",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "More than 1.5 million litres of petrol and diesel have been released for distribution so far from the oil terminal at Trincomalee, Manoj Gupta, Managing Director, Lanka IOC PLC said.",
        "He said fuel was filled to more than 100 bowsers up to date for distribution.",
        "However, he advised all dealers to ensure supplying fuel for ambulance without any delay and on priority basis. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
